== About Me


I'm currently a PhD Candidate at the [http://web.mit.edu/orc/www/ Operations Research Center] at [http://www.mit.edu MIT]. My research advisor is [https://cee.mit.edu/barnhart Professor Cynthia Barnhart]. I am the recipient of 2016-2017 UPS PhD Fellowship.

Before coming to MIT, I obtained my Bachelor's degree with summa cum laude in [http://www.ie.tsinghua.edu.cn/eng/ Industrial Engineering] from [http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/newthuen/index.html Tsinghua University], Beijing, in 2012, and my undergraduate thesis advisor was [http://www.ie.tsinghua.edu.cn/teacher/eview.php?Tid=52 Professor Hai Jiang].



